lead_paragraph: The swimmer, who won multiple medals at the 2012 Games, has her likeness plastered everywhere at the trials. But she has not yet qualified for the Rio Games.

headline.print_headline: At U.S. Olympic Trials, So Far at Least, Franklin Is Everywhere but Rio-Bound
headline.main: So Far at U.S. Olympic Trials, Missy Franklin Is Everywhere but on the Team

snippet: The swimmer, who won multiple medals at the 2012 Games, has her likeness plastered everywhere at the trials. But she has not yet qualified for the Rio Games.
abstract: American swimmer Missy Franklin, who won 5 medals at 2012 London Olympics and is face of United States' promotional campaign for 2016 Rio Games, has yet to qualify for team; pressure from high expectations is one potential reason for her lack of success so far.
